N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4624.19 - Time for filing lessor financial statement

State Regulations

Licensed games of chance lessors shall file form GC-9
with the licensing authority and commission within seven days after the
conclusion of each leased license period. Notes
